###############################################################################
##                                                                           ##
##       Makefile for oqeueDemo application of FreeRTOS on SCU-LM32          ##
##                                                                           ##
##---------------------------------------------------------------------------##
## File:    FreeRTOS/Demo/SCU_LM32_GCC/up-down_count/Makefile                ##
